      "question": "Do Monday & Tuesday really count as ONE trading day at Apex on holiday weeks?",
      "answer": "Yes. On holiday weeks Apex merges trades from the Sunday 6 p.m. open through the Tuesday session into a single \"trading day\" for evaluation-day counting and reporting.",
